title: Best Trends Forever 7/16: #DogsForBiden, Science, Birkin Bag, Jake Paul
itunes:title: Best Trends Forever 7/16: #DogsForBiden, Science, Birkin Bag, Jake Paul
description:
On this edition of Best Trends Forever Jack and Miles discuss a hashtag of people showing their dogs for Biden, the word "science" is trending because Kayleigh McEnany is saying "science shouldn't stand in the way" of kids going back to school (?!?!?!), Offset gave his child, Kulture, a Birkin Bag for her 2nd birthday, and Jake Paul is having a big party just because.
